Home now

I don't mind my brother staying with us for a while, but honestly I don't feel that close to him

I like hanging out with him, but sometimes
A lot of my free time, I wanna go on my computer, play games, watch youtube, [spoiler]and masturbate [/spoiler]
I just wanna relax on my own, I like doing that
But with my bro here, I have to hang out with him if he asks
Because I don't I might make him feel bad, the  I feel bad
Also my parents might get on my ass for spending all my free time on my computer and "not socializing", even though I'm an adult and am allowed to do what I want with my time


Oh and work was fine, though shitty traffic getting home
